              <div class="article-body">
                <p>Manufacturing isn’t a single process. It’s a system.</p>

                <p>
                  A part can move through die casting, surface prep, X-ray
                  inspection, CMM measurement, painting, masking, packaging, and
                  logistics before it is ready.
                </p>

                <p>
                  The real question for hardware brands is not whether to
                  outsource everything or build everything.
                </p>

                <p>
                  It is what you should control directly, and what you should
                  scale through trusted partners.
